</ul>
<p><a name="Hitler_in_media" id="Hitler_in_media"></a></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline">Hitler in media</span></h2>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;">
<div id="ogg_player_1" style="width: 180px;">
