<li><a href="http://www.eisenhower.archives.gov/Research/Digital_Documents/Holocaust/HitlerWillGeneralIntelligence.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.eisenhower.archives.gov/Research/Digital_Documents/Holocaust/HitlerWillGeneralIntelligence.pdf" rel="nofollow">"The Discovery of Hitler's Wills"</a> (<a href="/wiki/Office_of_Strategic_Services" title="Office of Strategic Services">Office of Strategic Services</a> report on how the testament was found).</li>
<li><a href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/07/21/AR2005072101680_5.html" class="external text" title="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/07/21/AR2005072101680_5.html" rel="nofollow">Matthew Brzezinski, "Giving Hitler Hell", Washington Post Sunday, July 24, 2005; p. W08</a> (Narrative of how the testament was found)</li>
</ul>
